The paper discusses the challenges and issues in cloud forensics, which involves security and privacy concerns (cs.CR), as well as the storage and retrieval of data in a cloud environment (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the need for regulatory compliance and audit trails, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and cyber security (cs.CY). Finally, the paper highlights the need for secure solution approaches, which could involve programming languages and compilers (cs.PL).
